Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.03,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You've all treated me very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:12.28,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,When I first arrived in the demon \Nworld, I was full of anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:15.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you gave me a very warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.53,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.79,Main,Claus,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mio-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.73,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But I've decided to live my \Nlife from here on as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:28.46,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't intend on succeeding my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:31.59,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.99,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.48,Main,Child,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:25.24,Episode Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fad(939,810)}"Between Reality and One's Own Truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.49,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,In regard to extracting the \NDemon Lord's power from Mio-sama...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.83,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.00,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.78,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Circumstances have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:33.91,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,We must.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.02,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:37.61,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:37.94,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.38,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Basara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.78,Main,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.22,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.27,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Dimensional fluctuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.52,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Gald?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.53,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,That technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:03.14,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,When Brynhildr appears, \Nit causes a dimensional fluctuation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,which is fired as a shock wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.54,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,It's a supersonic slash, \Nlike the cuts of a whirlwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.25,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,It caught me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.40,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.45,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Leohart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.77,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,And I even volunteered to lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.26,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,No, you truly did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.80,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Now get some rest, and heal your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.07,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Gald was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.61,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Naruse Mio shattered that heroic spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.06,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Ramsus presented a glimpse of his \Ntrue power for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.34,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,and that son of Jin Toujou...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...drove away Gald.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.07,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Leo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.47,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.35,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.26,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You look terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.22,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Did something unpleasant happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.46,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.73,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.68,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Your big sister Liala \Nsees through everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.73,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win against you, can I, Elder Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.68,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do the usual tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:40.25,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You're a splendid \NDemon Lord, Leo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.39,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You won't ever lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.76,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your big sister's on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:50.26,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of any bad people \Nwho try to get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.23,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.44,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I tripped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.28,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,That was rather extravagant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.88,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:18.29,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,The form of the competition will be \Na 7-on-7 match of representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:21.00,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever camp seizes the most victories
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,will obtain authority over the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:27.81,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Thus it has been decreed under the \Nname of the Demon Lord Leohart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.81,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you plan to do, Ram-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.31,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no doubt it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.06,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, the folks on the council
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:43.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't allow these conditions \Nwithout some kind of ploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.19,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:49.32,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,It's unsettling that it doesn't \Ntouch at all on the victor's prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.33,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The reward goes without \Nsaying: it's Mio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:57.36,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And the head of whoever \Nloses gets the axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:01.34,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's a lot better \Nthan waging full-scale war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.60,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine if that heroic spirit showed \Nup with a large army at its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.72,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The damage would be a lot worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.18,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.72,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Still, things never do go \Nquite as planned, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.36,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The new Demon Lord Leohart \Nbeing a man of such caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you calling Mio-chan here to the demon realm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,were both miscalculations, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.72,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:28.56,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the council would select a \NDemon Lord that was more easily manipulated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:30.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:34.77,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I went to our rendezvous \Npoint when things went down,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but "she" was nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.68,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any changes \Nin plans on your end, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:43.09,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,No, even I don't have a \Ngrasp on her whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.44,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:51.14,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Safia-chan doesn't seem to be \Nin the demon realm at all, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.92,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.89,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.68,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, well, you could say \Nit's a woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.24,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Your intuition's usually on target, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.78,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now, let's clear out the \Nproblems that are right before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:15.91,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do you plan on \Nfighting this competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.72,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't very well leave \Nit up to those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.51,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there, Ram-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.92,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I know Leohart was unexpected,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we head out ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire plan could be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:34.96,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:35.68,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.24,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.19,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll relieve you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:52.38,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, we still have some \Ntime before the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.90,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything I can to train them up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,till the final moment \Nbefore we have to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.21,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach them how they can win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.00,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.27,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You can put your decision off \Nuntil you see that through, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.00,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. If you can still \Nkeep it up, then come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.72,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.86,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard enough to \Ndodge attacks in mid-air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.36,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you doing challenging \Na power-type head on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.86,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.29,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You're swinging that wide \Nright after I told you not to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.96,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That one wasn't bad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.24,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,if you want to hit your target for certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to break your opponent's \Nguard with your feint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.14,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.15,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,you end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.54,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.29,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.36,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.56,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll resume after a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.85,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.17,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:14.03,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You've met the current \NDemon Lord Leohart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.82,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He seemed young, \Nbut he was quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:22.55,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I stand a chance \Nof beating him as I am now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.48,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.98,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you fight him head-on, \Nhe might be stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.98,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't beat him either?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.49,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up against someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.99,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I never said there's \Nno way for you to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.99,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all how you go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.45,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,How I go about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:49.12,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, you don't have \Na proper understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of what your own greatest strength is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:55.00,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'd rather take \Nmy time teaching it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't have much left to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.33,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You finished resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.76,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.68,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.80,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do this a little rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.29,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on, I'm going to \Ncome at you without holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.52,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,98...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.58,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,99...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.90,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more, Mio-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.52,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to a hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:01.53,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.79,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.78,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.56,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.30,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.30,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.31,Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.81,Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some magic water, \Nperfect for recovering your stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.84,Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.57,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-san, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.43,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Strengthening your basic physical abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:45.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is the most fundamental way \Nof raising your combat skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:49.30,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,If you raise your baseline well, \Nit's sure to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.70,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not enough for me as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.21,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be better at using \Nthe Demon Lord's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.28,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,otherwise I'll be a burden to Basara again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:04.00,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can do that overnight, \Nthen you're sorely mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:08.47,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But that man had no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.61,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Ramsus is Ramsus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.18,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,You are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:16.76,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hone your own strengths \Nbefore you focus on Wilbert's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.48,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.81,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.48,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.08,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.31,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mother, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.00,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.00,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Here, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.00,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.01,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.44,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.61,Main,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.52,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Your Master-Servant pact incites \Na succubus's state of arousal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I created a pill to suppress \Nthe curse's activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.68,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,But I have one warning for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.78,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,A warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.03,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,As your loyalty increases,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it will grow more difficult for you \Nall to ascertain Basara's position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.00,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:17.54,Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.36,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What? What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.85,Main,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,That came from Oldra Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.08,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.30,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.72,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.45,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give him some treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.84,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I took it a bit too far \Nwhen I cornered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.64,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:47.61,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.02,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.39,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.25,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.40,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.53,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,We finished treating you, but don't push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.76,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I thought I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:36.03,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, you think I'd \Nactually kill my cute boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:41.26,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was planning on pounding you enough \Nto keep you from moving for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.34,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.02,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You said you weren't holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.44,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I really was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.90,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.55,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Who would tell you that beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:54.25,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have an appreciation of \Ngaining the power by risking your own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:59.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,then you can't really place your \Nlife in its hands, now can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.95,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you think when you \Nwere on the verge of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.56,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:17.08,Flashback,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect everyone with \Nmy own power, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:22.74,Flashback,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell can I die here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.56,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,That's really all I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:31.32,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Good. And do you remember \Nthat move at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.00,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:33.59,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.21,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Then remember that sensation well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.64,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you need to imagine yourself activating that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.11,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,more consciously on your own, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:41.85,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.60,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,But that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.60,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.04,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.20,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The way it works is pretty close to when you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:53.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,lost control of your power and \Ncaused that tragedy at the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.54,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It comes from converting your erasure \Nenergy into a discharged attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.55,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.13,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.47,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.38,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Take deep breaths. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:35.89,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.10,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.66,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:44.81,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Basara, right now you have three \Nlimiters placed on your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.17,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,"Three limiters"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.57,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,A conscious one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a subconscious one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:56.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and one based on hatred of Brynhildr\N for helping cause that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.43,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to control \Nthe use of a demon sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:04.13,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If the wielder's not careful, it could\N influence his mind and consume him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:09.86,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,However, your aversion to that is also \Nplacing a limit on Brynhildr's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:15.09,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon you were\N pushed to the edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you didn't have time to think \Nabout your aversion to Brynhildr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.20,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That move's the result of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:26.56,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,In order to match up with Leohart, \Nyou'll need to release one of those limiters—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:30.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,two if possible—or you'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:33.71,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Two, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.37,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so pessimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:44.10,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,This coming battle isn't one \Nwhere you have to beat Leohart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.78,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:50.24,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Basara, what was your goal \Nin coming to the demon realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.86,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious. To protect Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:56.36,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you go and win against \Nthe reigning Demon Lord faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,then the moderate faction will start up \Ntheir cries again to make Mio-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the next reigning Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.09,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But if you lose, it'll all be over, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.37,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying to aim for a draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.29,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.32,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The place where you're looking for to settle things
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:14.29,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,is on a different field from victory or defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.16,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Then how am I supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:18.38,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.63,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:25.38,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work out, \Nthen I'll cover your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.99,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So go cut loose, Basara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.64,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.42,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.43,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,there's something I need \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.65,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:43.60,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's about your two mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.24,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.01,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:14.02,Flashback,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,In order to match up with Leohart, \Nyou'll need to release one of those limiters—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:17.89,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,two if possible—or you'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.69,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,If I release them, then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.20,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.21,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.07,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Basara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.92,Main,Shella,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.00,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.25,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I have a few requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.42,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Ramsus-sama and I will \Njoin up with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:36.25,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please be as careful as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.31,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.77,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.51,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.78,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.78,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
